{"title":"无风的夜","date":"2021-02-14T20:41:29.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 15, 2021","L":"02/15/2021","MM-DD":"02-15"},"author":"白桦","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/beach-1838331_640.webp","link":"2021/02/15/WindlessNight","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2021-02-15T05:06:51.641Z","content":"<p>风迎着我们<br>\n微凉却不寒厉<br>\n送来青草和<br>\n苹果一样的气息</p>\n<p>墨绿色的单车<br>\n他是如此顽皮<br>\n在这无人的路上<br>\n笑着，跑着</p>\n<p>我问：<br>\n天要黑了<br>\n要什么时候停下来</p>\n<p>他默不作声<br>\n我只好紧握<br>\n任他带我走过这<br>\n无风的夜</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Nginx Proxy Manager——小而美的多容器转发方案","link":"2021/02/27/NginXProxyManager"},"next":{"title":"Rewind 岁末旧片","link":"2020/12/31/Rewind"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2021/02/15/WindlessNight/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 15, 2021"},"reading_time":"81 words in 1 min"}